OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny morning fog patches soon
OL,6,Fclearing to mostly cloudy conditions,
OL,7,Falthough some sunny spells are likely
OL,8,Fto develop during the afternoon. Winds
OL,9,Fbecome light but breezy along the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBecoming cloudy overnight as
OL,13,Flow cloud and fog develops in the east
OL,14,Fof the region before spreading
OL,15,Fwestwards. Winds remain light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FWednesday sees low cloud
OL,18,Fand fog slowly lifting and clearing
OL,19,Fduring the morning, with some long
OL,20,Fbrighter spells developing later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
